{"tid":1262763,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"無恥的葉劉淑儀","createTime":"2019-06-28T00:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T12:14:25.000Z","uid":267572,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"86a3af50439a41e62cf8eafb5ebff3f83b74493d","tid":1262763,"uid":267572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:22:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sFh10PeJSFU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsFh10PeJSFU&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=f0a3e161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sFh10PeJSFU</a><br />\n<br />\n1。片中葉劉指李柱銘是等第一位動議要求中港兩地移交的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr98-99/chinese/counmtg/floor/981209cd.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr98-99%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Ffloor%2F981209cd.pdf&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=aadd1f94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr98-99/chinese/counmtg/floor/981209cd.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n葉劉YouTube 片指李柱銘嘅動議，係1998年12月9日的會議。見上面會議記錄124頁至128頁。<br />\n<br />\n閲讀理解：<br />\n<br />\n當時說在香港發生的刑事罪應該在香港審而不應在內地審。沒有說在大陸犯罪而潛逃來香港的要移送到大陸，即現惡法。<br />\n<br />\n第128頁動議內容：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;由於兩名富商在香港特別行政區(&ldquo;特區&rdquo;)被綁架案及德福花園五屍命案均在內地法院以《中華人民共和國刑法》審理，引起港人極大 關注，但特區政府卻未盡全力爭取將在特區境內涉嫌違法的人士，交 還特區法院審理，以捍 《基本法》賦予特區的司法管轄權，對此， 本會深表遺憾;同時，本會促請特區政府以國際社會公認的原則為基 礎，盡快就中港兩地移交疑犯的安排與中央人民政府進行商討及達成 協議，恢復港人對特區司法管轄權的信心。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n2。見片中，葉劉説當年23條不是撤回而是跟現在做法一樣。<br />\n<br />\n我不查看她說會議的記錄了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/brandhk/0905014.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2Fbrandhk%2F0905014.htm&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=2627259a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/brandhk/0905014.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n直接見上文政府新聞稿說撤回23條的。難道政府當時正式新聞稿錯！<br />\n<br />\n葉劉可䎵，斷章取義，誤導市民。<br />\n<br />\n7月1日要叫條賤人辭去立法議員一職。"},{"pid":"6b1f1cbdeb5be81057d52eb4a85e4b54af8cec9b","tid":1262763,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:53:31.000Z","msg":"🤦🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"a0fb00f2cf0b338974d34f38191f418a7b57b1df","tid":1262763,"uid":91017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:33:04.000Z","msg":"佢目的係點火, 佢想林鄭仆街,"},{"pid":"94dad11873f6dd06a2153dfce8e07442b9653d84","tid":1262763,"uid":147620,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:41:55.000Z","msg":"條片勁多好評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06899a0c110b1e1afb12fcc957427739dcffb993","tid":1262763,"uid":256014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">　　人會變，月會圓，時代變，巨輪轉，</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">　　雖然</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">２０１９０６１６</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">有</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">二百萬</span><span style=\"color: green;\">香港市民</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">遊行，</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">下次</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">遊行</span>並不代表也有<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">二百萬</span><span style=\"color: green;\">香港市民？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">　　而</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">遊行</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">人數</span>亦不代表<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">２０１９</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">區議會選舉</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">與及</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">２０２０</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">立法會選舉</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">之</span><span style=\"color: red;\">賽果，</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">　　約廿年前</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">的</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">事</span>摷出來講，唔怪得<span style=\"color: green;\">林鄭月娥</span>條死八婆管治下，<span style=\"color: brown;\">將</span><span style=\"color: green;\">北京</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">１９８９０６０４</span><span style=\"color: red;\">搬入</span><span style=\"color: green;\">香港</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">２０１９０６１２</span>（倒退管治）。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"d015426bf95a3a3654a873d79e55442703b29738","tid":1262763,"uid":71446,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:40:42.000Z","msg":"葉劉只係當香港係佢上位既舞台，香港人你死你事，don&rsquo;t give a shit。"},{"pid":"7887050f5b9aa8f1e302b6d7b7e3aef8dd738296","tid":1262763,"uid":260023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T04:22:45.000Z","msg":"葉劉你都傻傻地錯誤邊度你都唔知<br />\n有什麼資格做議員 <br />\n李柱銘 提議是香港人交還香港審理 <br />\n葉劉支持的香港人交畀中國虐殺抄家<br />\n 兩個分別不一樣<br />\n你也搞不清<br />\n蒙騙市民 <br />\n又多一個講大話拗著數的政棍"},{"pid":"37219f95c9ba428da6a822a39de8cde74eb8309c","tid":1262763,"uid":260023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06899a0c110b1e1afb12fcc957427739dcffb993","tid":1262763,"uid":256014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">　　人會變，月會圓，時代變，巨輪轉，</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">　　雖然</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">２０１９０６１６</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">有</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">二百萬</span><span style=\"color: green;\">香港市民</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">遊行，</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">下次</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">遊行</span>並不代表也有<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">二百萬</span><span style=\"color: green;\">香港市民？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">　　而</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">遊行</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">人數</span>亦不代表<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">２０１９</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">區議會選舉</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">與及</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">２０２０</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">立法會選舉</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">之</span><span style=\"color: red;\">賽果，</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">　　約廿年前</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">的</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">事</span>摷出來講，唔怪得<span style=\"color: green;\">林鄭月娥</span>條死八婆管治下，<span style=\"color: brown;\">將</span><span style=\"color: green;\">北京</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">１９８９０６０４</span><span style=\"color: red;\">搬入</span><span style=\"color: green;\">香港</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">２０１９０６１２</span>（倒退管治）。</strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T04:28:35.000Z","msg":"區議會選舉將出現一班 <br />\n不談政治<br />\n學了民建聯欺騙市民的新人<br />\n爭取和關注地區問題 <br />\n沒有政綱<br />\n沒有使命<br />\n只會空談和量血壓 <br />\n什麼漂書<br />\n我們就將香港寄託在這班區議員身上？"},{"pid":"e189adb21b80e3ddf4a4dada88d921b675ab5616","tid":1262763,"uid":264626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T04:31:11.000Z","msg":"fr apple daily:<br />\n<br />\n1998年立法會曾討論與內地作出的移交逃犯安排，時任保安局局長葉劉淑儀指出，香港和內地雙方訂有一項行政安排，以便內地有關當局把純粹在香港觸犯罪行的香港居民移交香港進行調查或審訊。香港政府在回歸後繼續與內地有關當局進行討論。鑑於內地與香港的法律及司法制度存在極大差異，故必須審慎行事，強調制訂香港及內地均能接受的移交逃犯安排，絕非一項簡單易辦的工作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會會議記錄：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr98-99/chinese/panels/se/minutes/se031298.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr98-99%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fse%2Fminutes%2Fse031298.htm&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=b0ead52f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr98-99/chinese/panels/se/minutes/se031298.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n根據會議記錄：<br />\n<br />\n葉劉講：當局早在回歸之前已和內地有關當局就移交逃犯安排展開<br />\n初步的討論，香港特區政府亦在回歸後繼續與內地有關當局進行討論。鑑於內地與<br />\n香港特區的法律及司法制度存在極大差異，當局必須審慎行事。制訂香港特區及內<br />\n地均能接受的移交逃犯安排，絕非一項簡單易辦的工作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年說要做公眾諮詢，如今就如林鄭的態度，總之反對的就是廢話！！！"},{"pid":"fdc169600f6e46bd8f35ff57092a529a02a06759","tid":1262763,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86a3af50439a41e62cf8eafb5ebff3f83b74493d","tid":1262763,"uid":267572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T00:22:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sFh10PeJSFU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsFh10PeJSFU&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=f0a3e161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sFh10PeJSFU</a><br />\n<br />\n1。片中葉劉指李柱銘是等第一位動議要求中港兩地移交的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr98-99/chinese/counmtg/floor/981209cd.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr98-99%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Ffloor%2F981209cd.pdf&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=aadd1f94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr98-99/chinese/counmtg/floor/981209cd.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n葉劉YouTube 片指李柱銘嘅動議，係1998年12月9日的會議。見上面會議記錄124頁至128頁。<br />\n<br />\n閲讀理解：<br />\n<br />\n當時說在香港發生的刑事罪應該在香港審而不應在內地審。沒有說在大陸犯罪而潛逃來香港的要移送到大陸，即現惡法。<br />\n<br />\n第128頁動議內容：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;由於兩名富商在香港特別行政區(&ldquo;特區&rdquo;)被綁架案及德福花園五屍命案均在內地法院以《中華人民共和國刑法》審理，引起港人極大 關注，但特區政府卻未盡全力爭取將在特區境內涉嫌違法的人士，交 還特區法院審理，以捍 《基本法》賦予特區的司法管轄權，對此， 本會深表遺憾;同時，本會促請特區政府以國際社會公認的原則為基 礎，盡快就中港兩地移交疑犯的安排與中央人民政府進行商討及達成 協議，恢復港人對特區司法管轄權的信心。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n2。見片中，葉劉説當年23條不是撤回而是跟現在做法一樣。<br />\n<br />\n我不查看她說會議的記錄了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/brandhk/0905014.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2Fbrandhk%2F0905014.htm&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=2627259a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/brandhk/0905014.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n直接見上文政府新聞稿說撤回23條的。難道政府當時正式新聞稿錯！<br />\n<br />\n葉劉可䎵，斷章取義，誤導市民。<br />\n<br />\n7月1日要叫條賤人辭去立法議員一職。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:19:28.000Z","msg":"咁其實A送B<br />\nB又可以唔送去A係唔公平既......<br />\n咁不如一切唔送囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00293a5cf0669dff8f24c1975b45d54c2a4132c3","tid":1262763,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"repl